text:
Bryan Cranston is in a new movie co-starring next to Kevin Hart.

In the movie they had the option to go paragliding for real, or do it in front of a green screen. Cranston tells Jimmy Fallon exactly how Hart acted after being only 15 feet in the air (in front of the green screen)!

Too funny!
title: Bryan Cranston Does An Impression Of Kevin Hart Freaking Out
